casebody.data:
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, AS TRUSTEE FOR J.P. MORGAN MORTGAGE ACQUISITION TRUST 2006-CH2 ASSET BACKED PASS-THROUGH CERTIFICATES, Series 2006-CH2, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Edward A. PROVENCHER, His/Her Heirs, Devisees, and Personal Representatives, and His, Her, Their or Any of Their Successors in Right, Title and Interest, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Mrs. Edward A. Provencher, Wife of Edward A. Provencher; et al., Defendants. C-450 September Term 2018
081714 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003747-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
